    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Magister Andrune Vesh — The Technocrat Candidate</h2>\n<p><em>Standard-reference Aerdy legal scholar. Honest. Out of options. His sister-in-law Lyla faces twenty years on customs forgery her late husband actually committed; Sereth is dangling private acquaintance with the prosecuting advocate as the price of the harbor commission seat.</em></p>\n<h3>Combat behavior</h3>\n<p>Non-combatant. Yields. The party's leverage on him is to remove the leverage on him.</p>\n<h3>Statblock summary (CR 1/2, PB +2)</h3>\n<p>AC 11 · HP 22 (5d8) · Speed 30 ft. · Init +0 · Passive Perception 13</p>\n<p>STR 9 · DEX 10 · CON 11 · INT 18 · WIS 14 · CHA 12. Saves: INT +6. Skills: History +6, Insight +4, Investigation +6.</p>\n<p>Languages: Common, Old Aerdi, Suloise, Aerdi imperial cipher.</p>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p><em>Blooming Rot, Part 2 — Phase 4.</em> See <em>The Three Seats → Magister Andrune Vesh — The Technocrat</em>.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
